snippet.title: Bugtime
snippet.description: Bugtime Shoot all the bugs before you run out of time!

snippet.title: Magma Mayhem
snippet.description: Magma Mayhem Dodge the falling magna, try to survive as long as you can. The longer you live, the higher your score.

snippet.title: GTO Drift
snippet.description: GTO Drift Get on the road and prove yourself as a worthy GTO driver collecting stars and drifting along.

snippet.title: Zombie at the Gates
snippet.description: Zombie at the Gates Action survival game. Use swords and bows to destroy attacking zombies while building a balloon.

snippet.title: Save My Tree
snippet.description: Save My Tree Puzzle game. Make sure the water droplet reaches the hose so the tree can grow again.

snippet.title: Soccer Ball
snippet.description: Soccer Ball Click on the ball repeatedly and try to keep it bouncing in the air as long as possible.

snippet.title: Ultimate Ping
snippet.description: Ultimate Ping This is a modified Break Out game. Try to keep the ball bouncing as long as you can.

snippet.title: Copter
snippet.description: Copter Lead the helicopter thru the digital cave for as long as you can.

snippet.title: Air Dodge
snippet.description: Air Dodge Keep your plane flying as long as possible. Avoid the balloons and other obstacles.

snippet.title: Chain Reaction
snippet.description: Chain Reaction Try to create a a chain reaction for as long as possible.
